Gemcraft Inc told shareholder annual meeting company principal shareholder repurchase 130000 share common stock. The company's portion repurchase obligation equal 800000 dlrs company plan record capital transaction 1987. Originally Gemcraft estimate require buy 300000 share 3.0 mln dlrs. Gemcraft originally estimate portion trading loss total 600000 dlrs record charge earnings amount 1986 fourth quarter. The company plan provide after-tax credit income 200000 dlrs quarter 1987 reflect difference. Gemcraft told shareholder see profitable 1987 quarter. In year-ago period report earnings 908000 dlrs 6 ct share sale 88.8 mln. Reuter 